metadata.name: Emergency
metadata.description:
"Imagine a big explosion as you climb through 3,000 ft. Imagine a plane full of smoke. Imagine an engine going clack, clack, clack. It sounds scary. Well I had a unique seat that day. I was sitting in 1D."

AI can visualize what we have said throughout human history. 

The first line of a famous speech prompts AI to reimagine the moment through its own language.

Can you see what AI is saying?
